        <strong>Alpha wave increase</strong>
        <p>200mg L-theanine increases alpha brain wave activity within 40 minutes. Alpha waves (8-13 Hz) are associated with calm alertness, creativity, and relaxed focus — the opposite of stress-driven beta wave dominance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>GABA + serotonin + dopamine</strong>
        <p>L-theanine simultaneously elevates three neurotransmitters: GABA (calming), serotonin (mood), and dopamine (motivation). This triple modulation explains its broad-spectrum calming-yet-uplifting effect.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>No sedation, no dependence</strong>
        <p>Unlike benzodiazepines or melatonin, L-theanine does not cause drowsiness, cognitive impairment, tolerance, or withdrawal. FDA GRAS status with no known toxicity ceiling at supplemental doses.</p>
      </div>
